Thorax: Pronotum and propleuron largely black, with pale streak below notopleural suture, pale lateral marks on anterior pronotal lobe, rear of middle pronotal lobe, laterally on posterior pronotal lobe. Dorsum of synthorax matte black with small pale mark between arms of anterior bifurcation of middorsal carina. Synthorax laterally with bright pale marks as follows (
Fig. 20
