Fig. 26
). Legs (posterior pair removed for DNA extraction): Coxae and trochanters pale with brown areas. Femora obscurely brown and grey. Tibiae and tarsi dark brown. Wings with arculus ca level of Ax 4 ( 5 in left Hw), quadrilateral with 1 crossvein in Fw, 2 in Hw, cubitoanal space free in all wings, pt brown. Wing membrane with brownish tint, extreme tips of both wings with slightly heavier brown tint.

